OL,4,CDumfries could be at risk of closure
OL,6,FDozens of rural schools across
OL,7,FDumfries and Galloway could be at risk
OL,8,Fof closure.
OL,10,FNew education guidelines mean that
OL,11,Fschools with a low occupancy rate
OL,12,Fcould be earmarked to close their
OL,13,Fdoors by the end of the year.
OL,15,FIn a review of all primary and
OL,16,Fsecondary schools across the region,
OL,17,FDumfries and Galloway Council's
OL,18,Feducation chiefs are proposing that
OL,19,Feach of the 114 schools should be
OL,20,Fevaluated.
