OL,3,CDozens of rural schools across
OL,4,CDumfries could be at risk of closure
OL,6,FEach must meet 10 requirements to
OL,7,Fsafeguard their future.
OL,9,FEducation bosses insist that the
OL,10,Fproposed new school model is essential
OL,11,Fto "future proof the schools estate"
OL,12,Fand meet Scottish Government
OL,13,Fobjectives.
OL,15,FThe 10 key principles which schools
OL,16,Fmust meet include factors related to
OL,17,Ftravelling distance for pupils and
OL,18,Fteacher staffing levels.
OL,20,FHowever, principle six is of most
OL,21,Fsignificance to rural schools.
