OL,3,CDozens of rural schools across
OL,4,CDumfries could be at risk of closure
OL,6,FIt details: "Schools should have an
OL,7,Foccupancy rate where possible greater
OL,8,Fthan 60% utilisation of the capacity
OL,9,Fof the school, and ideally should be
OL,10,Foperating at 80% utilisation."
OL,12,FAn education report published six
OL,13,Fmonths ago revealed that 47 out of the
OL,14,F98 primary schools fall below this 60%
OL,15,Ffigure, with two having an occupancy
OL,16,Frate of just 15%.
OL,18,FOf the 16 high schools, seven are
OL,19,Fbelow 60% occupancy.
