OL,6,FLarann Foss, the schools' property
OL,7,Fmanager with Dumfries and Galloway
OL,8,Fcouncil, produced the report which
OL,9,Fwill be presented to councillors.
OL,11,FHe described "significant challenges
OL,12,Fand risks for managing the school
OL,13,Festate over the coming years.
