OL,3,CDozens of rural schools across
OL,4,CDumfries could be at risk of closure
OL,6,FMr Foss said: "These include changing
OL,7,Fdemographics such as population
OL,8,Fdecline, residential development in
OL,9,Flocalised areas, ongoing deterioration
OL,10,Fin our building infrastructure,
OL,11,Fpressure on planned maintenance
OL,12,Fbudgets, increasing revenue expenses,
OL,13,Fthe presence of RAAC (reinforced
OL,14,Fautoclaved aerated concrete) in some
OL,15,Fschools and the expansion of early
OL,16,Fyears provision, to name but a few.
