OL,3,CDozens of rural schools across
OL,4,CDumfries could be at risk of closure
OL,6,F"The continued general deterioration
OL,7,Fof underutilised facilities also
OL,8,Frepresents an increasing risk of
OL,9,Fproperty component failure and
OL,10,Ffacility closure with very limited
OL,11,Fnotice e.g., a heating or roofing
OL,12,Ffailure."
OL,14,FMr Foss also underlined that the
OL,15,Fpopulation for youngsters aged 0-15 in
OL,16,FDumfries and Galloway is projected to
OL,17,Fdecline by 14% between mid-2018 and
OL,18,Fmid-2028.
