OL,3,CDozens of rural schools across
OL,4,CDumfries could be at risk of closure
OL,6,FHe wrote: "A focus on securing 'best
OL,7,Fvalue' has been required in recent
OL,8,Fyears where there is significant
OL,9,Fpressure on local authorities to make
OL,10,Fsavings where there are increasing
OL,11,Fdemands on public finances and
OL,12,Fservices, and we must acknowledge that
OL,13,Fthe costs-per-pupil in under-occupied
OL,14,Fschools are excessively high and that
OL,15,Funderutilised schools are expensive to
OL,16,Fmaintain and operate.
OL,18,F"The importance of future-proofing the
OL,19,Fschool estate in light of population
OL,20,Fdecline therefore cannot be
OL,21,Funderestimated."
