OL,6,FCouncillors will be asked to agree to
OL,7,Fa seminar for further explanation of
OL,8,Fthe proposed school model process.
OL,10,FIt is also proposed that another
OL,11,Freport should be brought back to the
OL,12,Fcommittee in December 2024, detailing
OL,13,Fpotential changes which would "move
OL,14,Fthe school estate to a sustainable
OL,15,Fposition."
